<header class="masthead text-center text-white">
  <div class="masthead-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="masthead-heading mb-0">Is It Good?</h1>
      <h2 class="masthead-subheading mb-0">A Simple But Powerful Rating Website</h2>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl rounded-pill mt-5">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
        <div class="p-5">
          <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="<%= asset_path('review.jpg') %>" alt="">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
        <div class="p-5">
          <h2 class="display-4">A flexible rating system...</h2>
          <p>Choose from existing categories such as Movies, TV Shows, Restaurants or suggest new categories which will be reviewed by admins.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="p-5">
          <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="<%= asset_path('to-do.jpg') %>" alt="">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="p-5">
          <h2 class="display-4">Set up to-do lists</h2>
          <p>Read some reviews and decided you'd like to save some ideas for later? Create a custom to-do list.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
        <div class="p-5">
          <img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="<%= asset_path('collection.jpg') %>" alt="">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
        <div class="p-5">
          <h2 class="display-4">Create collections</h2>
          <p>Want to create a collection of your favourite movies, your favourite songs, your favourite recipes? Create your own collection and open it up for reviews/suggestions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
